snippet.title: Donkey Kong Country (GBC) / Donkey Kong 2001 Japanese Commercial
snippet.description:
With their famous platformer portable AND in color, Donkey and Diddy celebrate on the dance stage. Roll (or somersault) on over to this translation for DKC2 2001's packaging: https://chrisaaronblog.blogspot.com/2024/06/donkey-kong-games-2000.html

My transcription of the audio:
あの、ドンキーとディディーが40のコースが大冒険！
新アイテムのグリーンバナナやミ二ゲームで、更に楽しい！
ゲームボーイカラー専用：ドンキーコング２００１
